    "description": "Xpressbees International Enterprises, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Marketplace Manager for our Gwalior operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Xpressbees International Enterprises:\nXpressbees International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Xpressbees International Enterprises!",
